          <rect class="kw-row" x="36" y="270" width="388" height="44" rx="6"></rect>
          <text class="kw-t" x="48" y="287">builds a KeywordContext and injects what handlers need:</text>
          <text class="kw-t" x="48" y="303">hand &middot; draw/discard piles &middot; energy &middot; EntityManager &middot; target cell</text>
          <text class="kw-t" x="36" y="336">KeywordHandlerRegistry resolves each tag &rarr; IKeywordHandler</text>

          <line class="kw-flow" x1="230" y1="350" x2="230" y2="384" marker-end="url(#kw-arrow)"></line>
          <text class="kw-t" x="242" y="372">yield each handler in order</text>

          <rect class="kw-box" x="20" y="390" width="126" height="62" rx="10"></rect>
